GET SETUP:

- INSTALL STUFF
  sudo apt-get install apache2
  sudo apt-get install php5 libapache2-mod-php5
  sudo apt-get install php5-mysql
  sudo apt-get install ant
  install mysql

- SETUP DATABASE
  create database icecoldn_jon;
  use icecoldn_jon;
  create user 'icecoldn_jonbri'@'localhost' identified by 'jbsi1985';
  grant all on *.* to 'icecoldn_jonbri'@'localhost';

- PREPARE LOCAL ENVIRONMENT
  check jon.properties
  creates deployment dirs in apache dir: 
  sudo ant deploy

- USEFUL COMMANDS
  To restart apache: 
  sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart"

